  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Rail Gun with Ion weapons<o:p></o=
:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Research Preference: Power and Shields<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The race originally called Ortain were a small
  grey-skinned reptilian race. The Ortain created machines in their own ima=
ge
  specifically to do jobs and work such as war that an Ortain could not do =
as
  efficiently.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The machines were created with complex AI and eventu=
ally
  were regarded as full members of the Ortain race. The Ortain machines sha=
red
  most of the same laws and had positions of power where they were suited.<=
o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Some event not described by history saw the Ortain w=
iped
  out as a species. <span class=3DGramE>However</span> the AI created by the
  Ortain lived on and filled the gaps in the jobs and power structure left =
by
  the death of their biological counterparts.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The machine Ortain were built for war and do not have
  feelings regarding comfort or personal space, this has allowed them to
  develop the Compact Troop Compartment, a smaller way to carry large amoun=
ts
  of infantry on their ships.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The machine Ortain are very paranoid and can be very
  insular in behavior. They are badly equipped for diplomacy or co-habitati=
on
  with other species. Often, Ortain fall back on their combative programmin=
g,
  considering it their job to subdue other races.</p>
